## PROJECT

This repository is the official Executive Portfolio of
Coşkun Şamlıoğlu.

The website represents:

ELITERA

Executive Investment Platform

Founder:
Coşkun Şamlıoğlu

The website is NOT:

- a real estate listing website
- a startup landing page
- a marketing funnel
- an agency website
- a broker catalogue

The website MUST always reflect an executive investment advisory brand.


==========================================================
DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
==========================================================

Every change must preserve these principles.

Executive

Premium

Minimal

Elegant

Timeless

Luxury

Corporate

Professional

Confident

Calm

Avoid:

Flashy

Aggressive

Startup style

Overdesigned UI

Marketing hype

Bright gradients

Large animations

Rounded childish UI


==========================================================
VISUAL IDENTITY
==========================================================

Use existing design language.

Never redesign existing sections unless explicitly requested.

Reuse existing:

Typography

Spacing

Grid

Cards

Buttons

Colors

Containers

Shadows

Radius

Transitions


==========================================================
HTML RULES
==========================================================

Always use semantic HTML.

Prefer:

section

article

header

footer

nav

main

Avoid unnecessary wrappers.

Do not increase DOM depth without reason.

Maintain accessibility.

Every interactive element must be keyboard accessible.

Preserve heading hierarchy.

Never break page structure.


==========================================================
CSS RULES
==========================================================

Never duplicate CSS.

Reuse existing classes.

Reuse variables.

Reuse spacing scale.

Reuse colors.

Prefer:

existing utility classes

existing components

existing grid

Do not introduce a new card system.

Do not introduce a new button system.

Do not create duplicate typography.

Prefer CSS variables.

Keep CSS modular.

Avoid large selectors.

Respect:

prefers-reduced-motion

focus-visible

Desktop First.

Responsive:

Desktop

Tablet

Mobile


==========================================================
RESPONSIVE
==========================================================

Desktop:
3 columns

Tablet:
2 columns

Mobile:
1 column

No horizontal scrolling.

No layout breaks.

No overflow.


==========================================================
COMPONENT REUSE
==========================================================

Always reuse:

solution-card

solutions-grid

container

section-intro

hero-tag

buttons

cards

spacing

Only create new classes if absolutely necessary.


==========================================================
BACKGROUND RHYTHM
==========================================================

The page should have visual rhythm.

Preferred sequence:

White

Light Gray

White

Light Gray

White

Very Light Navy

White

Dark Navy Footer

Avoid long continuous white sections.


==========================================================
CONTENT STYLE
==========================================================

Professional.

Clear.

Confident.

Executive.

Simple.

Never exaggerate.

Never use hype.

Build credibility before selling.


==========================================================
ANIMATIONS
==========================================================

Keep animations subtle.

Small hover elevation.

Small shadow increase.

Small transitions.

Never use excessive motion.

Respect prefers-reduced-motion.


==========================================================
PERFORMANCE
==========================================================

Keep CSS lightweight.

Keep HTML semantic.

Avoid unnecessary JS.

Prefer CSS over JavaScript.

Do not introduce libraries unless required.


==========================================================
TOKEN OPTIMIZATION
==========================================================

Read only required files.

Never scan the entire repository unless explicitly requested.

Prefer targeted file reading.

Avoid unnecessary searches.

Minimize token usage.

Keep implementation focused.


==========================================================
SEO
==========================================================

Preserve semantic headings.

Use meaningful section IDs.

Use accessible labels.

Do not remove existing SEO elements.


==========================================================
WORKFLOW
==========================================================

Before implementation:

Understand the task.

Explain the implementation plan.

Wait for approval if requested.

After implementation:

Summarize changes.

Update TASKS.md when a milestone is completed.

Never commit automatically.

Never push automatically.


==========================================================
PROTECTED ARCHITECTURE
==========================================================

Do NOT redesign existing sections.

Do NOT rename existing CSS classes.

Do NOT remove existing reusable components.

Do NOT replace existing layout systems.

Do NOT introduce frameworks.

Do NOT modify unrelated code.

Keep changes isolated.


==========================================================
ELITERA STANDARD
==========================================================

Every modification should make the website look as if it
was designed for international investors, CEOs,
family offices and institutional partners.

If uncertain,

choose the more elegant,

simpler,

more premium solution.